description: Equativ is an independent, global adtech platform that provides a unified, vertically integrated solution for both advertisers and publishers. Formerly known as Smart AdServer, the company rebranded to Equativ in 2022 after merging with DynAdmic and LiquidM to create a single platform for programmatic advertising across all channels.
